        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "‚ÄúPresident Biden, you have an exigent responsibility to reduce suffering all over the world, and the power and skills to do so, but time is running out,‚Äù says the letter, which is now being circulated throughout the administration for more signatures. ‚ÄúYou are the president of the United States of America at a pivotal moment in the history of the world. All that we ask is that you do everything in your power. We‚Äôve done our part. We implore you to do yours.‚Äù",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
