        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "‚Äã‚Äã‚ÄúOur house is on fire, and Manchin burned the stairs. Democratic leaders are walking away,‚Äù Levin told ",
