          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". ‚ÄúWe cannot. We must test the fire escape, find the fire extinguisher, tie some sheets together if we have to: Our lives depend on it.‚Äù",
