      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "While the average age of a U.S. senator is 64, and Biden is 79, the average staffer is much younger ‚Äî and will live through the consequences of their bosses‚Äô inaction.",
